\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \sigma_{1},\dots,\sigma_{m},-\sigma_{1},\dots,-\sigma_{m}\right\} $
\end_inset

 and hence 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
B=\begin{pmatrix}V & V\\
U & -U
\end{pmatrix}\begin{pmatrix}\Sigma & 0\\
